title: STATION 2 PASS-ON-09-21-2015 11:10 PM-Co. 2
content:
STATION PASS ON ENTRY [CO.2] DATE/TIME 09-21-2015 11:10 PM YOUR NAME John Peppel ISSUE GENERAL PASS-ON DESCRIPTION OF ISSUE A false call was received over our business lines tonight at 18:33 hrs. The call came from an internal phone line at station 44.  The caller said "Box, 1098 Ruatan St"  (301) 559-2112
PG Batt 4 and the station 44 OIC has been contacted for investigation.
